cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of unlabeled data and proposes a new method for constructing a relational graph, which involves machine learning techniques such as robust aggregation and outlier detection. Therefore, it is likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well. Additionally, the paper involves multi-view information and identification challenges, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) respectively.
